An ATM is a machine built into the wall of a bank or other building that allows people to take money out of their bank accounts by using a special card. ATM is an abbreviation for “automated teller machine.” Atm are find any complex or mall
Everything seems to be going to be one of the best years. Everything starts on the good side. Who thought you could come across an Atm that wishes you a happy New year? A lady woke up and decided to go to the ATM to withdraw some money. She was surprised when the ATM opened and said, “Here is to a wonderful new year.” She went on to reveal that she was even scared that she might not get her money back. Some went on to say that other banks need to do better.
